originalText.text: I was originally referred to Karina for a grieving massage after my mother passed and it was exactly what I needed.  That was 7 months ago and since that time I’ve become a regular client because I like the personalized attention Karina gives to each session.  I like that at the beginning of the session she can already sense how I’ve been sleeping, if I’m staying hydrated, and if I’ve been stretching because it gives me the sense that she is concerned on a holistic level about my well-being.  She pays attention to my body and focuses each massage session on whatever problem areas I want to focus on.  I appreciate that Karina takes the time to explain things to me in a way that I can understand and she creates a welcoming and calming environment.

originalText.text:
Karina is an excellent massage therapist. I have been seeing her for a few months now and each visit she has been able to alleviate pain and discomfort in my muscles, help relieve the tension in the joint issues I’ve had for 20 years.
She’s very knowledgeable, caring and passionate in attending to her clients needs, and stays fully engaged in helping to remedy their issues.

originalText.text: Karina has been working on me weekly for almost a year. She’s amazing and knows exactly what my body needs and can pinpoint tension even when I cannot. I can’t recommend her enough, she’s nurturing as well and always sensitive to whatever is happening in my body. Can’t recommend her enough!

originalText.text: I recently had my first massage from Karina. She is truly amazing. Her work is very focused, and reflects her extensive knowledge of the body and of different treatment modalities. She made me feel very comfortable and relaxed, and was able to really help with a shoulder injury that has been causing me a lot of pain and discomfort. I am excited in advance for my next massage with her, and I could not recommend her more highly. Lastly, FWIW, I myself am an experienced, licensed massage therapist, and my standards are very high.

originalText.text: Karina is an expert in her industry. Her work is not only physical but spiritual. She is in-tune with the needs of your body, intuitively picking up on the necessary points, whilst working on you. Not only does she do phenomenal healing work, she also services & gives back to her community utilizing her art. She is a hidden gem in the healthcare industry and I wish her continued success performing this groundbreaking work. Thank you for your service!
